pageContext.claim: “My actions saved countless jobs across Ohio and here in Toledo, the home of the jeep, right? The home of the Jeep. That's good, that's a great brand. That saved a great brand with Jeep, Jeep.”
pageContext.analysis: Jeeps are made in Toledo but Trump did not "save" any jobs there.  Fiat Chrysler did announce a new Jeep plant -- in Detroit.
